Subject: [PATCH] drm/mgag200: Store flags from PCI driver data in device structure
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: d6d437d97d54c85a1a93967b2745e31dff03365a
